<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4775696>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 5–6. Photographs of the newly described Bleptus michinokuensis sp. nov. and Bleptus fasciatus under an optical microscope. Wings (5A), lateral view of body (5B), lateral view (5C) and ventral view (5D) of terminus of abdomen including genitalia of a male of B. michinokuensis sp. nov.; ventral view (6) of the terminus of abdomen including genitalia of a male B. fasciatus. Ce: cercus, Fc: forceps, FW: fore wing, HW: hind wing, PnL: penis lobe, VIII−X: 8th to 10th segments. Scale bars: 5A, 5B = 10 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4775696/files/figure.png" .

